{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "team7-modul2-flow",
    "name": "Modul 2 - Flow Test (2 Request)",
    "description": "Test Modul 2 cukup 2 request yang saling terhubung:\n\n1. Cari jadwal dengan semua filter → hasil sudah include available_seats\n2. Cek detail kursi untuk jadwal teratas dari hasil pencarian (ID otomatis diambil)\n\nCara pakai:\n- Import file ini + Postman_Environment.json\n- Klik Run (Runner) → Run Sequence → kedua request jalan otomatis berurutan",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Step 1 - Cari Jadwal (Semua Filter + Info Kursi)",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "// ✅ Cek response berhasil",
              "pm.test('Status 200 OK', function () {",
              "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
              "});",
              "",
              "// ✅ Cek response punya data",
              "pm.test('Response punya field data', function () {",
              "  const json = pm.response.json();",
              "  pm.expect(json).to.have.property('data');",
              "  pm.expect(json.data).to.be.an('array');",
              "});",
              "",
              "// ✅ Cek setiap jadwal sudah punya info kursi",
              "pm.test('Setiap jadwal punya available_seats & is_available', function () {",
              "  const json = pm.response.json();",
              "  if (json.data.length > 0) {",
              "    const first = json.data[0];",
              "    pm.expect(first).to.have.property('available_seats');",
              "    pm.expect(first).to.have.property('is_available');",
              "  }",
              "});",
              "",
              "// ✅ Simpan ID jadwal pertama untuk Step 2",
              "const json = pm.response.json();",
              "if (json.data && json.data.length > 0) {",
              "  const firstId = json.data[0].id;",
              "  pm.environment.set('schedule_id', firstId);",
              "  console.log('ID jadwal pertama tersimpan:', firstId);",
              "} else {",
              "  console.warn('Tidak ada jadwal ditemukan — coba ubah filter (date, origin, dll)');",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/schedules?origin_station_id=1&destination_station_id=5&only_available=true&sort_by=price&sort_dir=asc&per_page=5",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["api", "v1", "schedules"],
          "query": [
            {
              "key": "origin_station_id",
              "value": "1",
              "description": "ID stasiun asal — sesuaikan dengan data di DB kamu"
            },
            {
              "key": "destination_station_id",
              "value": "5",
              "description": "ID stasiun tujuan — sesuaikan dengan data di DB kamu"
            },
            {
              "key": "date",
              "value": "2026-05-01",
              "description": "Tanggal keberangkatan — nonaktifkan jika ingin ambil semua tanggal",
              "disabled": true
            },
            {
              "key": "time_from",
              "value": "06:00",
              "description": "Jam mulai keberangkatan",
              "disabled": true
            },
            {
              "key": "time_to",
              "value": "20:00",
              "description": "Jam akhir keberangkatan",
              "disabled": true
            },
            {
              "key": "train_type",
              "value": "eksekutif",
              "description": "ekonomi | bisnis | eksekutif",
              "disabled": true
            },
            {
              "key": "max_price",
              "value": "500000",
              "description": "Harga maksimum tiket",
              "disabled": true
            },
            {
              "key": "only_available",
              "value": "true",
              "description": "Hanya tampilkan yang masih ada kursi"
            },
            {
              "key": "sort_by",
              "value": "price",
              "description": "departure_time | price | duration_minutes"
            },
            {
              "key": "sort_dir",
              "value": "asc",
              "description": "asc | desc"
            },
            {
              "key": "per_page",
              "value": "5",
              "description": "Jumlah hasil (kecilkan agar lebih cepat)"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "Cari jadwal dengan filter. Response sudah include `available_seats` dan `is_available` di setiap item — tidak perlu hit /seats satu per satu.\n\nSetelah request ini selesai, ID jadwal teratas otomatis tersimpan ke environment variable `schedule_id` untuk dipakai di Step 2."
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Step 2 - Cek Detail Kursi (ID dari Step 1)",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "// ✅ Cek response berhasil",
              "pm.test('Status 200 OK', function () {",
              "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
              "});",
              "",
              "// ✅ Cek struktur response kursi",
              "pm.test('Response punya field data.available_seats', function () {",
              "  const json = pm.response.json();",
              "  pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('total_seats');",
              "  pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('booked_seats');",
              "  pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('available_seats');",
              "  pm.expect(json.data).to.have.property('is_available');",
              "});",
              "",
              "// ✅ Cek logika: total = booked + available",
              "pm.test('total_seats = booked_seats + available_seats', function () {",
              "  const d = pm.response.json().data;",
              "  pm.expect(d.total_seats).to.equal(d.booked_seats + d.available_seats);",
              "});",
              "",
              "// Log hasil",
              "const d = pm.response.json().data;",
              "console.log('Jadwal ID:', d.route_id);",
              "console.log('Kereta:', d.train);",
              "console.log('Kursi tersedia:', d.available_seats, '/', d.total_seats);"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/schedules/{{schedule_id}}/seats",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["api", "v1", "schedules", "{{schedule_id}}", "seats"]
        },
        "description": "Cek detail kursi untuk jadwal yang ID-nya otomatis diambil dari hasil Step 1.\n\n`{{schedule_id}}` diisi otomatis oleh test script di Step 1 — tidak perlu isi manual."
      }
    }
  ]
}
